(d) incorporate the Software or a modified version into any product, service,
    workflow, internal tool, hosted service, or other software distributed or
    operated for anyone other than yourself for Personal Use;
(e) use the Software or its contents to train, fine-tune, evaluate, benchmark,
    or operate an AI model or Automated System in an Organizational Use
    context; or
(f) direct an Automated System, contractor, or other intermediary to perform
